This repository is a collection of simple tools that can save time executing daily routines.
1. phone - discover office phone number of a colleague.
2. lab-db-search.pl - retrieve info about lab equipment
3. update_db.pl - update the lab db
4. create_vm_openstack.sh - placed in the directory with the keystonerc_admin file, tests the newly deployed RHOS setup by launching an instance. 
